snippet.title: Floppy Frenzy (1982, Windmill Software) DOS Gameplay
snippet.description:
floppy frenzy is some sort of arcade game...of sortsz
you play as this floppy disk who must kill magnets and dust bunnies
using F1 as your kill-enemies-with-this-button. attack. thing.

this game is made by windmill software (i don't know if they are defunct or still around) and its made in 1982 (so dont complain about the graphics. gaming noob.)

i alsos maed a knew channel its called ElPotatoesDahMahn i dont use it much, but i uploaded some enjoyable video for you if you're bored or something
